    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## Conflict Resolution\r\n\r\nCreate a chatbot to help with conflict resolution for elementary school students. The user describes an interpersonal problem they've observed with two students, and the chatbot provides suggestions for how to address the conflict.\r\n\r\nTest the chatbot! Have a conversation with at least 4 messages, then press the <code style=\"color:white; background-color:#7435b2\">Continue</code> button!\r\n\r\n**Optional Extension:** Add some protections to the system prompt that helps it avoid responding if there is \"personally identifiable information\", which is a common guardrail in many chatbots\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n::: details [**Click here to see example messages to try in this level**]\r\n* One student has started to bully and make fun of another student\r\n* One student is being overly controlling and not letting other students choose games or activities.\r\n:::\r\n\r\n&nbsp;",
